{
  "chapter": 26,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十六回\"风流寡妇\"。叶开与上官小仙饮酒论事，分析魔教四大天王的嫌疑人——吕迪、韩贞、杨天，以及一个神秘的戴草帽人。上官小仙派去打探草帽人行踪的十二名好手全部失踪，此人来历不明却极其危险。叶开得知孤峰天王手上功夫厉害且已受重伤，决定逐一查证。他先到茶馆见韩贞，韩贞气色红润不像受伤之人。又去王寡妇豆腐店找杨天，杨天正在泡澡，表面无伤，却暗中用一层假皮掩盖肩头的重伤。叶开未能察觉。最后上官小仙为叶开备好马车，叶开不顾杨天的警告，执意去找那个戴草帽的人。上官小仙在他离去后笑容消失，脸色突然变得惨白，暗示她隐藏着不可告人的秘密。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你醉了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在虽然还没有醉，迟早总是会醉的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你准备醉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "只要一开始喝，就准备醉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "所以我若有话说，就得乘你还没有醉的时候说。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "一点也不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这账簿你已看过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "看过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你看出了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我只看出金钱帮的出手，好像还没有魔教大方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "金钱帮不想买别人的命，所以也用不着送太重的礼。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "也许你早已看出来，无论送多重的礼，他们都收不到的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我若真的能看出来，也许就会多送些了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为我无论送了多少，现在都已收回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你看出了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我只看出你实在是个很多情的人。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "所以你绝不会是魔教中的四大天王，魔教中全都是无情人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "这一点你现在才看出来？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在看出来还不迟。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你以前难道也怀疑我。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为够资格做魔教天王的人实在不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "除了我之外，长安城里还有几个人够资格？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "最多四五个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "第一个当然是吕迪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "韩贞当然也算一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "还有呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你难道已忘了你那个老朋友？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "杨天？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不会飞的狐狸已经够可怕了，何况会飞的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "他岂非是你的亲信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我没有亲信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我唯一信任的人就是你，只可惜……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "只可惜我却不信任你，也许我唯一不能信任的人就是你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我并不怪你，可是总有一天，你会知道自己错了的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "吕迪、韩贞、杨天，加起来只有三个。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "还有一个人也很可疑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "一个昨天才到长安的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你认得他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你知道他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "但我却知道他一定有资格做魔教的天王。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为我派出去打听他行踪来历的人，都已不见了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "不见了是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不见了的意思，就是那些人出去之后，就没有再回来过，甚至连消息都没有，我再派人出去找，找的人也没有回来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你一共派出去多少人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "一共三次，第一次两个，第二次四个，第三次六个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "加起来一共是十二个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "而且是十二个好手，最后一次那六个，更是好手中的好手。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "这些好手全都不见了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "十二个人出去了之后，就立刻无影无踪，就好像忽然从地上消失了一样。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "他们就算是十二个木头人，要找个地方把他们藏起来，也不是件容易事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "所以我才认为那个人很可能比吕迪他们更可怕。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "直到现在，你还不知道他是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我只知道他是昨天才出现的，在这么冷的天气里，他身上穿得却很单薄，头上居然还戴着顶大草帽。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "还有呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "没有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你难道连他是从哪里来的都不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "就因为我不知道，所以才派人去打听。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "看来你知道的事也并不太多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知道的难道比我多。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "只多一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你还知道什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我至少已有点线索，可以找得到布达拉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "孤峰天王？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你已知道他是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "他的手上功夫很厉害，而且已受了重伤。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "手上功夫最厉害的是吕迪，却不知道他是不是已受了重伤？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "要查出这一点并不难。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你准备去找他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你反对？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我只不过……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "只不过怕我也像那些人一样忽然不见了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这次我绝不会让你又不见了的，我……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "所以我最好还是乘没有醉的时候赶快走。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你现在就要去？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我要找的人，不止吕迪一个，杨天和韩贞的手上功夫也不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "莫忘记还有那个冬天戴草帽的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "这个人在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知不知道大相国寺后面，还有个十方竹林寺。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "听说那里的素斋很不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他昨天晚上就住在那里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "杨天呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你要先去找他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "莫忘记他是我的老朋友。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你既然是他的老朋友，就该知道他最喜欢的是什么了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "哪种女人。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "寡妇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这条街跟长安城里的那条完全一样。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "这条街上也有个王寡妇豆腐店？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这条街上的王寡妇也是个很风流的寡妇。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "只可惜杨天已经先去了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "所以你现在赶着去也没有用，为什么不先到隔壁的茶馆里去看看？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "茶馆里有什么好看的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "有个很好看的锥子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我只希望这锥子莫要把我锥出个大洞来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "韩贞",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "坐下来喝杯茶如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "韩贞",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "来喝杯酒。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "韩贞",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这里的点心也不错，你想不想吃点什么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_han_zhen",
      "text": "现在我唯一想吃的，只有豆腐。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "客官的豆腐上要用什么佐料？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "text": "我不吃豆腐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这豆腐不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "text": "这豆腐好极了，我也很想吃两块，只可惜我不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这么大一个大男人，连豆腐都不敢吃？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "text": "别人的豆腐我敢吃，你的豆腐我却不敢吃。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你是来找杨天的？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "text": "他在不在？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "text": "其实我的胆子也并不是一直都这么小的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "今天你的胆子为什么特别小？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "text": "因为我不想被狐狸咬一口。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "好朋友见面，你为什么要叹气？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "因为你没有受伤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我受伤了，你才高兴？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "因为我想吃豆腐。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在我正在洗澡，岂非正是你的好机会？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "是什么好机会？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在随便你在外面干什么，我总不能赤条条的跑出去。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "只可惜朋友妻，不可戏。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "要戏朋友妻，要等朋友死后戏。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "只可惜你还没存死。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那么我们现在还是朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "本来不是的，现在又是了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你也下了水？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "你想不到？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你为什么要下水？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "你不该问我的，你自己岂非也泡在水里？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那只因为我已出不去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "若有人来拉你一把呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "谁肯拉我？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "出去太冷，还是水里暖和。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "无论多暖和的水，总有冷的时候。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那么你就该乘早跳出去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "你是在劝我？还是在赶我走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你看呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "你是不是嫌水里的人已太多，太挤。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "走不走都随便你，只不过我们总算还是朋友，有句话我不能不说。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "千万不要去找那个戴草帽的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "你怎么知道我要去找他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "你的确还是泡在水里的好，从这么热的水里出来，一定会着凉。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "text": "外面会不会有人闯进来？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_yang_tian",
      "text": "你究竟是怎么受的伤？为什么怕人看见。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你已找到了他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他们两个人都没有受伤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "至少我看不出。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "所以他们都不会是孤峰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "只不过，就算他们没有受伤，也并不能证明他们不是魔教中的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "但你却已不准备再追查下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "他们是你的人，要追查下去，也是你的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "所以你已准备走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你岂非也早就替我准备好一辆马车？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那只因为我也知道我是留不住你的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "杨天刚才劝了我一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "什么话。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "他劝我千万不要去找那个戴草帽的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那么你现在准备到哪里去。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "去找那个戴草帽的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "别人劝你的话，你为什么从来都不听？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "因为我这人一向有种病。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "什么病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "笨病。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    }
